                                <expan>Schwanne<ex>m</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_434_r1l13">doch ſo wöllet Jr Jn v̈mb
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> mit bete hilfflich ſeın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_434_r1l14"><expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dancken vvir
